data.description: A picturesque, two-story home! Built with a country style wrap around front porch. A screened in patio and gazebo overlooking a scenic pool on acreage and close to town. The pool has a salt chlorinator system, shaded wading area, a hot tub with waterfall,  all surrounded by pavers overlooking the oak laden 3 acres. Inside the home boasts a chef's kitchen, a cooktop grill, stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops and a huge pantry. The whole house has an instant hot water system, grill, dryer, pool heater powered by propane. The living room has an open 20+ ft ceiling, a secluded downstairs master bedroom w/ separate his and hers walk-in closets, large private master bath with a flat screen TV for relaxing while in the Jacuzzi tub or watching the news in the glass-encased walk-in shower. Upstairs includes two large bedrooms with a shared full bathroom and a third large bedroom which has its own private full bathroom. Above the oversized 2 car garage there is a very large 1 BR/1 BA apartment which is plumbed for a full kitchen; currently being utilized as a game/media room.
data.whatILove: The neighborhood and the neighbors. Everyone here is very friendly and down to earth. We are close enough to go to Fort Myers area or Clewiston if we need to but far enough away we do not deal with the crowds or the traffic. Peaceful semi-country living!
